No, I didn't.

50:30.540 --> 50:33.800
A-Adam, that's... that's really stupid.

50:33.800 --> 50:36.180
You see? This is why we broke up.

50:36.180 --> 50:38.680
I still can't believe you don't like Ghost in the Shell.

50:38.680 --> 50:41.100
Oh my God, are you guys talking about Ghost in the Shell?

50:41.100 --> 50:44.220
That is one of the most important movies ever made.

50:44.220 --> 50:45.640
I mean, it's a good movie.

50:45.640 --> 50:46.640
It's a good movie.

50:46.640 --> 50:47.640
It's a good movie.

50:47.640 --> 50:48.640
It's a good movie.

50:48.640 --> 50:49.640
It's a good movie.

50:49.640 --> 50:50.640
It's a good movie.

50:50.660 --> 50:51.840
It's one of the best movies ever made.

50:51.840 --> 50:53.340
I cannot wait to see it.

50:53.340 --> 50:56.000
This is a game that just made you unskippably

50:56.000 --> 50:58.880
go on a walking tour of a floor of this building.

50:58.880 --> 51:00.840
They took their sweet fucking time.

51:00.840 --> 51:01.840
Why can't I?

51:01.840 --> 51:04.140
I mean, the guy's name is Bateau.

51:04.140 --> 51:06.260
The French word for boat.

51:06.260 --> 51:08.640
