51:41.620 --> 51:43.900
The couple you can save at the manufacturing plant

51:43.900 --> 51:45.200
are a great example too,

51:45.200 --> 51:48.000
but I especially like the way Zeke Sanders is used.

51:48.040 --> 51:49.500
Not because the pre-rendered cutscene

51:49.500 --> 51:51.340
